headline.main: JAMES M'N WHISTLER DIES IN LONDON; Celebrated American Artist Unexpectedly Passes Away. He Was Born in Lowell, Mass., in 1834 -- Entered West Point -- Some of His Well-Known Works.

snippet: LONDON, July 18 -- James Abbott McNell Whistler, the celebrated American artist, died yesterday afternoon at his residence, 74 Cheyne Walk, Chelsea at the age of sixty-nine years. His death came unexpectedly, although for some time he had been ser...
